-- Jacob Zuma Appoints Deputy Ministers of Education, Energy in South Africa
-- B y   R e n e e   B o n o r c h i s
-- 2010-10-31T15:58:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-31/jacob-zuma-appoints-deputy-ministers-of-education-energy-in-south-africa.html
South African President Jacob Zuma
said he has appointed deputy ministers of education, performance
monitoring and energy, without naming them.  Zuma made the comments to reporters in Pretoria today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Renee Bonorchis in Johannesburg at 
